{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onloadend","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Свойства</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload\"><code>onload</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>onloadend</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart\"><code>onloadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"ru\"><span>Свойство</span></span>&nbsp;<strong><code>onloadend</code></strong>&nbsp; <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"ru\"><span>от </span></span><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> примесь <code><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"ru\"><span>передаёт код для вызова в момент возникновения события</span></span> <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code>&nbsp; (когда процесс загрузки ресурса окончился и остановился)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Синтаксис","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>img</var>.onloadend = <var>funcRef</var>;\n</pre>\n\n<p>При возникновении события&nbsp; <code>loadend</code>&nbsp; будет вызвана функция обработчик&nbsp;<code>funcRef</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>myImage.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 'loadstart' fires first, then 'load', then 'loadend'</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'load'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image loaded'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'loadstart'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image load started'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'loadend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Image load finished'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Спецификации","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onloadend\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ru\">Определение 'onloadend' в этой спецификации.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Живой стандарт</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Поддержка браузерами","id":"поддержка_браузерами","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onloadend","dataURL":"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Синтаксис","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Примеры","id":"example"},{"text":"Спецификации","id":"specification"},{"text":"Поддержка браузерами","id":"поддержка_браузерами"}],"summary":"Свойство onloadend  от GlobalEventHa